      <title>[Gem] How to make --no-ri --no-rdoc the default for gem install?</title>
      <link>http://blog.kerkerj.in/blog/gem-how-to-make---no-ri---no-rdoc-the-default-for-gem-install/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2013 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://blog.kerkerj.in/blog/gem-how-to-make---no-ri---no-rdoc-the-default-for-gem-install/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;In home dir, create a file: .gemrc (on linux, maybe on mac)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;echo &amp;quot;gem: --no-ri --no-rdoc&amp;quot; &amp;gt;&amp;gt; ~/.gemrc
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
</description>
